Vous pouvez consulter cette <a href="https://support.ankama.com/hc/fr/categories/200093427" target="_blank"><u><font color=''#ffd376''>page</font></u></a> et respecter toutes les consignes de sécurité qui permettent de sécuriser son compte.<br>', 'You have just received an Internet or e-mail address.
It may be an attempt to steal your DOFUS account.<br>
You should ONLY give out your login details on the official website: <b><a href="http://www.dofus.com"><u><font color=''#ffd376''>www.dofus.com</font></u></a></b>.<br> 
